## Stack Recommendations â€” Best Fit for the Codebase

> [!TIP]
> These recommendations align with your existing Express 5 + React 19 + Neon DB stack and are the best fit for production-grade vault & blockchain features.

### 1. Vault Storage Engine
| Component | Current | Recommended |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| Database | Neon PostgreSQL | âś… **Keep** â€” ACID transactions are critical for financial ledger integrity |
| Balance precision | `DECIMAL(14,4)` | âś… **Keep** â€” 4 decimal places for sub-gram precision |
| Concurrency | No locking | âš ď¸Ź **Add** `SELECT FOR UPDATE` on balance changes to prevent race conditions |

### 2. Blockchain Layer
| Component | Current | Recommended |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| Hash function | SHA-256 (`crypto.createHash`) | âś… **Keep** â€” industry standard, LBMA-compatible |
| Chain structure | DB-backed linked list | âś… **Keep** for private chain, but add **Merkle tree verification** for audit |
| Hash weakness | `Date.now()` in hash input | âš ď¸Ź **Fix** â€” use `crypto.randomUUID()` for nonce, not timestamp |
| Public blockchain | None | đź†• **Optional** â€” anchor weekly Merkle roots to **Stellar/XLM** (best fit for asset tokenization, used by SureRemit, already popular in Nigeria) |

### 3. Token System
| Component | Current | Recommended |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| Token standard | Custom DB-backed | âś… **Keep** for internal NIBMX-Au |
| Maker-Checker | Built, but duplicate routes | âš ď¸Ź **Consolidate** [vault.mjs](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/kibx/api/_routes/vault.mjs) tokens + [tokens.mjs](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/kibx/api/_routes/tokens.mjs) into single [tokens.mjs](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/kibx/api/_routes/tokens.mjs) |
| API-first standard | Custom | đź†• Consider **ERC-1155 compatible metadata** format for future interop |

### 4. Security Hardening
| Area | Recommendation |
|------|---------------|
| **Rate limiting** | Add `express-rate-limit` to vault deposit/withdraw/transfer (10 req/min) |
| **Audit logging** | Use existing `logAudit` middleware on ALL vault mutation endpoints |
| **Input validation** | Add `zod` schemas for weight/amount validation (positive, max limits) |
| **Transaction atomicity** | Wrap multi-table vault ops in `BEGIN...COMMIT` (PostgreSQL transactions) |
| **API versioning** | Prefix `/api/v1/vault/*` for future breaking changes |

### 5. Frontend Enhancements
| Feature | Recommendation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Real-time price** | Connect to **Gold API** or **MetalpriceAPI** for live XAU/NGN spot |
| **Chart library** | Add **Recharts** (already React-compatible) for vault balance graphs |
| **QR codes** | Use **qrcode.react** for printing gold passport QR tags |
| **PDF export** | Use **@react-pdf/renderer** for vault statement / passport certificates |
| **Push notifs** | Use existing notification system, add **Web Push API** for real-time alerts |

